titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: TPRG-SEND TWO YEAR CORRECTED AGE OUTCOME ASSESSMENT SCORE (NEUROMOTOR QUESTION E) - Description

div.p: TPRG-SEND TWO YEAR CORRECTED AGE OUTCOME ASSESSMENT SCORE (NEUROMOTOR QUESTION E) is the PERSON SCORE for question E of the Neuromotor section of the TPRG-SEND Two Year Corrected Age Outcome Assessment.
The question asks "Is this child unable to sit?".
